          "type": "text",
          "size": "t",
          "text": [
            "This book is an experiment with Markov Chains. I force-fed a computer Grimms' fairy tales and asked it to come up with a new tale."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "size": "t",
          "src": "/media/grimmer/funny.webp",
          "alt": "Funny Illustration"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "size": "t",
          "text": [
            "The result was a hilariously entertaining read and proof of how good even a very basic model such as Markov Chain can be."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "size": "t",
          "src": "/media/grimmer/Pg2.webp",
          "alt": "Page 2 Illustration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "size": "t",
          "text": [
            "Once I generated the text, I illustrated it in the style of children's story books.",
            "I then printed and bound the book to give it some physicality and dimensionality."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "size": "t",
          "src": "/media/grimmer/cover.webp",
          "alt": "Grimmer Book Cover"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
